29	Page	3	update	\N	---\nid: 3\ncontent: "<!-- intro -->\\n<div class=\\"mt-2 pb-0 bg-glass\\">\\n  <div class=\\"container-fluid\n  p-5\\">\\n    <h2 class=\\"text-center fw-bold\\">WE ARE LARKS\\n    </h2>\\n    <h5 class=\\"text-center\\">\\n\n  \\     We are young, dynamic and self managed agency with creative minds. We develop\n  and provide effective communication solutions with strategic foresight, passion\n  and creativity\\n    </h5>\\n    <button type=\\"button\\" class=\\"btn glass-button\\"\n  data-bs-toggle=\\"modal\\" data-bs-target=\\"#exampleModal\\">\\n      Take a Look!\\n\n  \\   </button>                \\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n<!-- vision  -->\\n<div class=\\"p-5\n  pt-0 pb-0 bg-glass\\">            \\n  <div class=\\"row mt-4\\">\\n    <div class=\\"wrapper\\">\\n\n  \\     <div class=\\"verticalBar verticalBarLeft\\">\\n        <div class=\\"text\\">OUR\n  VISION\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\"line\\">\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\n  \\   </div>\\n    <div class=\\"col-lg-6 col-xs-12 order-2 order-lg-1\\">\\n      <!--\n  <p class=\\"text-start fs-6 text-decoration-underline\\" style=\\"letter-spacing: 2px;\\">-\n  ABOUT US</p> -->\\n      <h2 class=\\"text-start pt-4 ps-4\\">We are in the business\n  of improving a long-term engagement to dynamic metamorphosis by quality solutions\n  and opportunities at the highest level.\\n      </h2>                    \\n    </div>\\n\n  \\   <div class=\\"col-lg-6 col-xs-12 order-1 order-lg-2\\">\\n      <img src=\\"./assets/vision.svg\\"\n  class=\\"d-block w-100 h-75\\" alt=\\"larks services\\">\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n<!--\n  story  -->\\n<div class=\\"p-5 pt-0 pb-0 bg-glass\\">            \\n  <div class=\\"row\n  mt-4\\">\\n    <div class=\\"wrapper\\">\\n      <div class=\\"verticalBar verticalBarLeft\\">\\n\n  \\       <div class=\\"text\\">OUR STORY\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\"line\\">\\n\n  \\       </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\"col-lg-6 col-xs-12 order-1\n  order-lg-1\\">\\n      <img src=\\"./assets/story.svg\\" class=\\"d-block w-100 h-75\\"\n  alt=\\"larks services\\">\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\"col-lg-6 col-xs-12 order-2\n  order-lg-2\\">\\n      <!-- <p class=\\"text-start fs-6 text-decoration-underline\\"\n  style=\\"letter-spacing: 2px;\\">- ABOUT US</p> -->\\n      <h1 class=\\"text-start\\">How\n  we got started\\n      </h1>\\n      <p class=\\"text-start pt-3 fs-6\\">                        \\n\n  \\       Welcome to LARKS, your number one source for all things. We're dedicated\n  to providing you the very best solutions.\\n        Founded in 2013 by group of friends/developers,\n  LARKS has come a long way from its beginnings in bangalore. When we first started\n  out, our passion for building software products that help for mankind and provide\n  best solutions drove them to start their own business.\\n        We hope you enjoy\n  our products and solutions as much as we enjoy offering them to you.\\n        <!--\n  LARKS company started in year 2013 and started exploring on how to simplify the\n  things that are used in daily life. On exploring solutions we came across how to\n  reduce human difficulty. we came up with an idea of ERP and started to build software\n  for schools. Going forward we created ERP for schools for web, What we had thinked\n  earlier was diffrent from when we started developing, as we develop we will be getting\n  more ideas. In 2016 Web had launched but we found something was incomplete that\n  was Mobile App. We started to create Mobile friendly app which will be ease to use\n  for the same application. Now we are in Mobile and Web Era and succesfully launched\n  both. We dint stop thinking, Now we are thinking and developing on how we can make\n  system more intelligent to understand human needs. -->\\n      </p>                   \\n\n  \\   </div>\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n<!-- process  -->\\n<div class=\\"p-5 pt-0 pb-0 bg-glass\\">\n  \\          