oping on how we can make system\n  more intelligent to understand human needs. -->\\n            </p>\\n        </div>\\n\n  \\   </div>\\n</div>\\n<!-- process  -->\\n<div class=\\"p-5 pt-0 pb-0 bg-glass\\">\\n\n  \\   <div class=\\"row mt-4\\">\\n        <div class=\\"wrapper\\">\\n            <div\n  class=\\"verticalBar verticalBarLeft\\">\\n                <div class=\\"text\\">OUR\n  PROCESS\\n                </div>\\n                <div class=\\"line\\">\\n                </div>\\n\n  \\           </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\"col-xs-12 mx-auto\\">\\n\n  \\           <ol class=\\"process-chart\\">\\n                <li class=\\"bg-glass text-dark\\">\\n\n  \\                   <div class=\\"bg-glass text-dark\\">\\n                        <h3>DISCOVER\\n\n  \\                       </h3>\\n                        <p class=\\"text-start pt-3\n  fs-6\\">\\n                            Develop a thorough understanding of the project,\n  audience, and objectives to formulate a digital strategy.\\n                        </p>\\n\n  \\                   </div>\\n                </li>\\n                <li>\\n                    <div>\\n\n  \\                       <h3>DESIGN\\n                        </h3>\\n                        <p\n  class=\\"text-start pt-3 fs-6\\">\\n                            Craft a purposeful\n  design to reflect the objectives and indicate the direction for the entire project.\\n\n  \\                       </p>\\n                    </div>\\n                </li>\\n\n  \\               <li>\\n                    <div>\\n                        <h3>IMPLEMENT\\n\n  \\                       </h3>\\n                        <p class=\\"text-start pt-3\n  fs-6\\">Bring the design to life in the form of an interactive and functional prototype.\n  Review, refine and optimise.\\n                        </p>\\n                    </div>\\n\n  \\               </li>\\n                <li>\\n                    <div>\\n                        <h3>DEVELOP\\n\n  \\                       </h3>\\n                        <p class=\\"text-start pt-3\n  fs-6\\">Incorporate implementation and technical components into a highly functional\n  system, ready for review.\\n                        </p>\\n                    </div>\\n\n  \\               </li>\\n                <li>\\n                    <div>\\n                        <h3>DELIVER\\n\n  \\                       </h3>\\n                        <p class=\\"text-start pt-3\n  fs-6\\">Review, refine, test and prepare final product for delivery. Launch and continue\n  to evolve over time.\\n                        </p>\\n                    </div>\\n\n  \\               </li>\\n            </ol>\\n        </div>\\n    </div>\\n</div>\\n<!--\n  team  -->\\n<div class=\\"p-5 pt-0 bg-glass\\">\\n    <div class=\\"row mt-4\\">\\n        <div\n  class=\\"wrapper\\">\\n            <div class=\\"verticalBar verticalBarLeft\\">\\n                <div\n  class=\\"text\\">OUR TEAM\\n                </div>\\n                <div class=\\"line\\">\\n\n  \\               </div>\\n            </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\"col-lg-3\n  col-xs-12\\">\\n            <div class=\\"card bg-glass mobile-margin\\">\\n                <div\n  class=\\"card-body p-3 text-white\\">\\n                    <h5 class=\\"mb-0\\">Lohith\\n\n  \\                   </h5>\\n                    <hr />\\n                    <p class=\\"fs-6\\">Team\n  Member\\n                    </p>\\n                    <small>\\n                        <a\n  href=\\"mailto:admin@larks.in\\" class=\\"text-decoration-none text-white\\">lohith@larks.in\\n\n  \\                       </a>\\n                    </small>\\n                </div>\\n\n  \\           </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\"col-lg-3 col-xs-12\\">\\n\n  \\           <div class=\\"card bg-glass mobile-margin\\">\\n                <div class=\\"card-body\n  p-3 text-white\\">\\n                    