        <div class=\\"verticalBar verticalBarLeft\\">\\n\n  \\               <div class=\\"text\\">OUR TECHNOLOGIES\\n                </div>\\n                <div\n  class=\\"line\\">\\n                </div>\\n            </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div\n  class=\\"row\\">\\n            <div class=\\"col-lg-3 col-xs-12\\">\\n                <blockquote\n  class=\\"blockquote blockquote-custom bg-glass p-3\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"blockquote-custom-icon\n  bg-rails shadow-sm\\"><img src=\\"/uploads/asset/attachment/56/ruby.svg\\" class=\\"img-fluid\n  p-2\\" alt=\\"Ruby on Rails\\"></div>\\n                    <p class=\\"mb-0 mt-2 fw-bold\n  text-white\\">Ruby on Rails</p>\\n                </blockquote>\\n\\n            </div>\\n\n  \\           <div class=\\"col-lg-3 col-xs-12\\">\\n                <blockquote class=\\"blockquote\n  blockquote-custom bg-glass p-3\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"blockquote-custom-icon\n  bg-rails shadow-sm\\"><img src=\\"/uploads/asset/attachment/57/react.svg\\" class=\\"img-fluid\n  p-2\\" alt=\\"Ruby on Rails\\"></div>\\n                    <p class=\\"mb-0 mt-2 fw-bold\n  text-white\\">React Js</p>\\n                </blockquote>\\n\\n            </div>\\n\n  \\       </div>\\n    </div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<!-- story  -->\\n<div class=\\"p-5 pt-0 bg-glass\\">\\n\n  \\   <!-- design -->\\n    <div class=\\"row mt-4\\">\\n        <div class=\\"wrapper\\">\\n\n  \\           <div class=\\"verticalBar verticalBarLeft\\">\\n                <div class=\\"text\\">WHAT\n  WE PROVIDE\\n                </div>\\n                <div class=\\"line\\">\\n                </div>\\n\n  \\           </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\"col-lg-4 col-xs-12 order-1\n  order-lg-1\\">\\n            <img src=\\"/uploads/asset/attachment/35/designdetail.svg\\"\n  class=\\"d-block w-100 h-75\\" alt=\\"larks services\\">\\n        </div>\\n        <div\n  class=\\"col-lg-8 col-xs-12 order-2 order-lg-2\\">\\n            <!-- <p class=\\"text-start\n  fs-6 text-decoration-underline\\" style=\\"letter-spacing: 2px;\\">- ABOUT US</p> -->\\n\n  \\           <h1 class=\\"text-start\\">DESIGN\\n            </h1>\\n            <div\n  class=\\"row\\">\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-4 col-xs-12 mobile-margin\\">\\n\n  \\                   <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n                        <div\n  class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5 class=\\"card-title\n  fw-bold\\">UX Research\\n                            </h5>\\n                            <hr\n  />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start fs-6\\">\\n                                It’s\n  important to research deeply for the product you want to build. We help in\\n                                that\n  by defining the user audience, working on user stories, competitive\\n                                analysis\n  and much more.\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n\n  \\                   </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-4\n  col-xs-12 mobile-margin\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n\n  \\                       <div class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5\n  class=\\"card-title fw-bold\\">UX Auditing\\n                            </h5>\\n                            <hr\n  />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start fs-6\\">\\n                                If\n  you are unsure of how your app behaves, we can help by doing a detailed UX\\n                                audit\n  that will highlight most of the issues in your product. From there, we can\\n                                take\n  it further and fix all issues.\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n\n  \\                   </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-4\n  col-xs-12 mobile-margin\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n\n  \\                       <div class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5\n  class=\\"card-title fw-bold\\">UX Consultation\\n                            </h5>\\n\n  \\                           <hr />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start\n  fs-6\\">\\n                                If you don’t know what kind of service\n  to request from us, don’t worry. We can\\n                                help and\n  see what fits your business and your budget.\\n                            </p>\\n\n  \\                       </div>\\n                    </div>\\n                </div>\\n\n  \\           </div>\\n        </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <!-- development -->\\n    <div\n  class=\\"row mt-4\\">\\n        <div class=\\"col-lg-8 col-xs-12 order-2 order-lg-1\\">\\n\n  \\           <!-- <p class=\\"text-start fs-6 text-decoration-underline\\" style=\\"letter-spacing:\n  2px;\\">- ABOUT US</p> -->\\n            <h1 class=\\"text-start\\">DEVELOPMENT\\n            </h1>\\n\n  \\           <div class=\\"row\\">\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-6 col-xs-12\n  mobile-margin\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n                        <div\n  class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5 class=\\"card-title\n  fw-bold\\">Web development\\n                            </h5>\\n                            <hr\n  />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start fs-6\\">\\n                                Technical\n  solutions of diffrent complexity are applied in all stages of web\\n                                development\n  process. As a result, you get highly competent digital product ready\\n                                to\n  use.\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n                    </div>\\n\n  \\               </div>\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-6 col-xs-12 mobile-margin\\">\\n\n  \\                   <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n                        <div\n  class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5 class=\\"card-title\n  fw-bold\\">Mobile development\\n                            </h5>\\n                            <hr\n  />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start fs-6\\">\\n                                A\n  whole world can be found on our mobile devices nowadays. That's why we deal\\n                                with\n  both native and cross platform applications broadening the horizons of\\n                                accessibility\n  by each smartphone click.\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n\n  \\                   </div>\\n                </div>                        \\n            </div>\\n\n  \\           <div class=\\"row mt-2\\">\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-6 col-xs-12\n  mobile-margin\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n                        <div\n  class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5 class=\\"card-title\n  fw-bold\\">Front End development\\n                            </h5>\\n                            <hr\n  />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start fs-6\\">\\n                                We\n  are deep focused Front End masters. The result of our work is a responsive, accessible,\n  and performant websites. Either you have the design ready and want us to code it,\n  or you want us to do both design and code, we’re happy to do so.\\n                            </p>\\n\n  \\                       </div>\\n                    </div>\\n                </div>\n  \\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-6 col-xs-12 mobile-margin\\">\\n                    <div\n  class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n                        <div class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n\n  \\                           <h5 class=\\"card-title fw-bold\\">Machine Learning /\n  AI \\n                            </h5>\\n                            <hr />\\n                            <p\n  class=\\"text-start fs-6\\">\\n                                The future is now. We\n  follow the rapid growth of technical industry and encourage you to do the same.\n  Bring your boldest ideas to us and let's transform the unbelievable to reality together.\\n\n  \\                           </p>\\n                        </div>\\n                    </div>\\n\n  \\               </div> \\n            </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\"col-lg-4\n  col-xs-12 order-1 order-lg-2\\">\\n            <img src=\\"/uploads/asset/attachment/37/developmentdetail.svg\\"\n  class=\\"d-block w-100 h-75\\" alt=\\"larks services\\">\\n        </div>\\n    </div>\\n\n  \\   <!-- infrastructure -->\\n    <div class=\\"row mt-4\\">\\n        <div class=\\"col-lg-4\n  col-xs-12 order-1 order-lg-1\\">\\n            <img src=\\"/uploads/asset/attachment/39/infradetail.svg\\"\n  class=\\"d-block w-100 h-75\\" alt=\\"larks services\\">\\n        </div>\\n        <div\n  class=\\"col-lg-8 col-xs-12 order-2 order-lg-2\\">\\n            <!-- <p class=\\"text-start\n  fs-6 text-decoration-underline\\" style=\\"letter-spacing: 2px;\\">- ABOUT US</p> -->\\n\n  \\           <h1 class=\\"text-start\\">INFRASTRUCTURE\\n            </h1>\\n            <div\n  class=\\"row\\">\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-6 col-xs-12 mobile-margin\\">\\n\n  \\                   <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n                        <div\n  class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5 class=\\"card-title\n  fw-bold\\">Managed CloudOps\\n                            </h5>\\n                            <hr\n  />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start fs-6\\">\\n                                We\n  manage your cloud infrastructure and operations leveraging the latest\\n                                technologies\n  and methodolgies, including configuration management, automated\\n                                scaling,\n  self healing and continous deployment. Taking adavantage of our\\n                                experience\n  and DevOps process, we migrate and provide your team the 24/7 support\\n                                they\n  require to stay ahead.\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n\n  \\                   </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-6\n  col-xs-12 mobile-margin\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n\n  \\                       <div class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5\n  class=\\"card-title fw-bold\\">Cloud Consulting\\n                            </h5>\\n\n  \\                           <hr />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start\n  fs-6\\">\\n                                We work with organizations to help them\n  understand and formulate a strategy for\\n                                how they\n  adopt DevOps and cloud computing. We help with the architectural,\\n                                technical,\n  compliance and governance issues to make your journey painless.\\n                            </p>\\n\n  \\                       </div>\\n                    </div>\\n                </div>\\n\n  \\           </div>\\n            <div class=\\"row mt-2\\">\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-6\n  col-xs-12 mobile-margin\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n\n  \\                       <div class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5\n  class=\\"card-title fw-bold\\">Cloud migration\\n                            </h5>\\n\n  \\                           <hr />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start\n  fs-6\\">\\n                                we partner with organizations and help\n  them to create a migration plan that meet\\n                                thier\n  need to learn and evolve. Our solution covers the governance, compliance\\n                                and\n  security need of regulated industries.\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n\n  \\                   </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <div class=\\"col-lg-6\n  col-xs-12 mobile-margin\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"card bg-glass h-100\\">\\n\n  \\                       <div class=\\"card-body text-white\\">\\n                            <h5\n  class=\\"card-title fw-bold\\">Maintainence\\n                            </h5>\\n                            <hr\n  />\\n                            <p class=\\"text-start fs-6\\">\\n                                Adding\n  uptime and error monitoring ensures you will know about problems before\\n                                your\n  customer do. As data and feedback roll in, we can be on-hand to address\\n                                changes\n  or maintainence\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n\n  \\                   </div>\\n                </div>\\n            </div>\\n        </div>\\n\n  \\   </div>\\n</div>\\n"\nsite_id: 1\nname: services.html\npath: "/services"\nlayout_id: 1\ncreated_at: 2021-06-28 12:08:22.964931000 Z\nupdated_at: 2021-07-08 11:21:14.806086000 Z\n	2021-07-08 11:21:46.376675
